Package: gglabeller
Type: Package
Title: Shiny gadget for labelling points in ggplots
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alicia Schep
Maintainer: Alicia Schep <aschep@gmail.com>
Description: The gglabeller package has only one exported function, gglabeller,
    which generates a shiny gadget for interactively selecting points to
    label. It positions labels using the ggrepel package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: 
  R (>= 3.3)
Imports:
  shiny (>= 0.13),
  miniUI (>= 0.1.1),
  ggplot2 (>= 2.2.0),
  ggrepel (>= 0.6.8),
  stats,
  utils
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
